TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT PRODUCTS.PRODUCT_NUM, PRODUCTS.PRODUCTNAME, PRODUCTS.CATEGORY, PRODUCTS.PRICE, PRODUCTS.LASTMODIFIED FROM PRODUCTS where PRODUCTS.LASTMODIFIED > TO_DATE( '$$V_LAST_RUN', 'MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS')

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DIMPRODUCTS.SURROGATEKEY as SURROGATEKEY, DIMPRODUCTS.PRODUCTNAME as PRODUCTNAME, DIMPRODUCTS.CATEGORY as CATEGORY, DIMPRODUCTS.PRICE as PRICE, DIMPRODUCTS.STARTDATE as STARTDATE, DIMPRODUCTS.ENDDATE as ENDDATE, DIMPRODUCTS.CHGE_CURRENT_IND as CHGE_CURRENT_IND, DIMPRODUCTS.LASTMODIFIED as LASTMODIFIED, DIMPRODUCTS.PRODUCTID as PRODUCTID FROM DIMPRODUCTS WHERE CHGE_CURRENT_IND ='Y'

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(NOT ISNULL(LKP_PRODUCTID) AND LKP_PRODUCTNAME != PRODUCTNAME AND LKP_CHGE_CURRENT_IND = 'Y' , 'TRUE', 'FALSE')
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: UPDATE_REC

GROUP.DESCRIPTION: Path for the data when none of the group conditions are satisfied.
GROUP.NAME: DEFAULT1
